WHO   — The Aes Sedai — the White Tower and its seven colors
WHAT  — The women of the White Tower who wield saidar, divided into seven Ajahs by color and purpose.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the White Tower of Tar Valon  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — They are the Tower's hand in the world, sorting cause and Power across every color of purpose against the Shadow.
HOW   — They channel saidar bound by the Three Oaths sworn on the Oath Rod, which marks them with agelessness.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Seven colors of one Tower, bound by oath and set apart by the ageless face it gives.

